" which we define to be"
msgstr ""
"``train_one_epoch()`` 函數執行策略梯度的一個「週期（epoch）」，我們將其定義為"

#: ../../spinningup/extra_tf_pg_implementation.rst:137
msgid ""
"the experience collection step (L62-97), where the agent acts for some "
"number of episodes in the environment using the most recent policy, "
"followed by"
msgstr ""
"經驗收集步驟（L62-97），智慧體使用最新的策略在環境中執行若干回合，接著是"

#: ../../spinningup/extra_tf_pg_implementation.rst:139
msgid "a single policy gradient update step (L99-105)."
msgstr "單次策略梯度更新步驟（L99-105）。"

#: ../../spinningup/extra_tf_pg_implementation.rst:141
msgid ""
"The main loop of the algorithm just repeatedly calls "
"``train_one_epoch()``."
msgstr "演算法的主迴圈只是反覆呼叫 ``train_one_epoch()``。"

